instruction: Generate a recipe that's easy to make and good for health.
output: A healthy, easy-to-make recipe is a Quinoa Salad with Avocado, Corn and Lime. This recipe requires only 6 ingredients and takes less than 30 minutes to prepare. It is loaded with nutritious ingredients like quinoa, avocado, corn, lime, diced tomatoes and fresh herbs. It is a great option for a light lunch or dinner.
